According to Civil Engineering Director, Ms Lindiwe Silolo, the entire system comprising three waterlines feeding the Skietbaan reservoir, will be up and running by the end of the week. The particular waterline has been leaking for over 12 months. Mhluzi, a portion of Aerorand, Gholfsig and Roberts Estate was affected. • Get you latest cope of the Middelburg Observer for the full story.